# 情報科学04

## if文

```java
if (a > 5) {
	System.out.println("Hello")
} else {
	System.out.println("Good bye...!")"
}

```

ex1.) Turning.java

```java
class TurningIf {
	private static void p(String i) {
		System.out.println(i);
	}
	public static void main(String args[]) {
		if (args.length != 1) {
			p("Please Input one number!");
			System.exit(1);
		} else {
			int a = Integer.parseInt(args[0]);
		}
		if (a == 10) {
			p("a -eq 10");
		} else {
			p("a -ne 10"")
		}
	}
}
```

ex2) Eleseif.java

```java
class Elseif {
	private static void p(String i){
		System.out.println(i);
	}
	public static void main(String args[]) {
		if (args.length != 1) {
			p("Please Input one number!");
			System.exit(1);
		} else {
			int a = Integer parseInt(args[0]);
		}
		if (a < 0) {
			p("a < 0");
		} else if (a > 0) {
			p("a > 0");
		} else {
			p("a == 0");
		}
	}
}
			
			

```
